Robert Brubaker https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Robert_Brubaker 0 Robert Brubaker (October 9, 1916 – April 15, 2010) was an American character actor best known for his roles in television and movie westerns, including Gunsmoke and 40 Guns to Apache Pass.
